FBIS4-68185 "jptot021__l94051" JPRS-TOT-94-021-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 14 May 1994 WEST EUROPE GREECE Bomb Destroys Environment Ministry Car Bomb Destroys Environment Ministry Car NC1405061594 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 0400 GMT 14 May 94 NC1405061594 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Greek BFN [Text] A homemade device exploded at 2330 yesterday, under a car of the Environment, Town Planning, and Public Works Ministry that was parked on the corner of Ippokratis and Fanariotis streets, and destroyed it completely. The organization Furious Rebellion [Lissasmeni Andarsia] claimed responsibility for the explosion in a phone call to private television station SKY.
